file.name: double-reference.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Double reference
  version: '1.0'
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    colour:
      type: object
      required:
        - red
        - green
        - blue
        - alpha
      properties:
        red:
          type: integer
        green:
          type: integer
        blue:
          type: integer
        alpha:
          type: integer
    ColourValue:
      nullable: true
      $ref: '#/components/schemas/colour'
    ColourCollectionValue:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/ColourValue'
    Response:
      oneOf:
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ColourValue'
        - $ref: '#/components/schemas/ColourCollectionValue'
